<br>
When I run with a healer who buffs my energy resist for 8%, and I turn on my energy resist song for 20%, my energy resist from buffs sticks at 20%.  It does not rise to 26% (20+8=28 capped at 26).<br>
<br>
Also, when I turn off the song, isn't the base resist buff from the healer/shaman cancelled, even if its 10 minute timer is not up? <p>-------------------------------------------------------------------
